{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853536801,"sessionID":"ses_286e1bb78ffeDD1gceH5pBUr8o","part":{"id":"prt_d791e85fd001U3wOrN5woMvbKV","messageID":"msg_d791e717b001VZn1yp1ck4yn7p","sessionID":"ses_286e1bb78ffeDD1gceH5pBUr8o","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-14bc9fe03a3645978f1f2ca33bd82e08","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-013\n- **Title**: Redis 存储实现\n- **Module**: pkg/store\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nImplement the Redis storage provider for the AgentCube session store interface.\n\n## Dependencies\n- AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n\n## Related Changes\nNone","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/CHANGE.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/CHANGE.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775853536787,"end":1775853536798}}}}
