{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853546244,"sessionID":"ses_286e1bb78ffeDD1gceH5pBUr8o","part":{"id":"prt_d791eaaea001PB6ViKOlNlbscL","messageID":"msg_d791e86820011VOwq89tPtre8j","sessionID":"ses_286e1bb78ffeDD1gceH5pBUr8o","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-ff73e11193d944509e0df9cdebfc0153","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-013 Delta-Spec\n\n## Purpose\nImplement the Redis storage provider for the AgentCube session store interface, providing a concrete implementation of the Store interface defined in AR-012.\n\n## Base Specs\n- AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n- deployment/client-go.md: Kubernetes client library for runtime API types\n- session-store/design.md: Session store design including Store interface and Redis implementation\n- session-store/spec.md: Session store specification with detailed requirements\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Redis client initialization\nThe system SHALL initialize a Redis client using `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` with configuration from environment variables.\n\n#### Scenario: Basic Redis client setup\n- **GIVEN** valid `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` environment variables\n- **WHEN** the Redis store is initialized\n- **THEN** a Redis client is created with the configured address and password\n\n### Requirement: Store interface implementation\nThe system SHALL implement the Store interface using Redis client for all required methods.\n\n#### Scenario: Ping method implementation\n- **GIVEN** a healthy Redis connection\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n- **THEN** it returns nil after successful PING command\n\n#### Scenario: GetSandboxBySessionID implementation\n- **GIVEN** a session key exists in Redis\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, id)` is called\n- **THEN** it retrieves and unmarshals the SandboxInfo JSON\n\n#### Scenario: StoreSandbox implementation\n- **GIVEN** a valid SandboxInfo\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** it stores the JSON and updates indices atomically\n\n### Requirement: Environment variable configuration\nThe system SHALL read and validate Redis connection parameters from environment variables.\n\n#### Scenario: Missing required environment variables\n- **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is not set\n- **WHEN** Redis store initialization is attempted\n- **THEN** it returns an error indicating the missing required variable\n\n### Requirement: Error handling\nThe system SHALL properly handle Redis errors and convert them to appropriate package-level errors.\n\n#### Scenario: Redis connection error\n- **GIVEN** Redis server is unreachable\n- **WHEN** any store operation is called\n- **THEN** it returns a connection error\n\n#### Scenario: Key not found\n- **GIVEN** a session key does not exist in Redis\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID` is called\n- **THEN** it returns `ErrNotFound`\n\n### Requirement: Atomic operations\nThe system SHALL use Redis pipelines for multi-command operations to ensure atomicity.\n\n#### Scenario: StoreSandbox atomicity\n- **GIVEN** a valid SandboxInfo\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` executes\n- **THEN** all Redis commands execute in a single pipeline\n\n### Requirement: Connection lifecycle\nThe system SHALL properly manage Redis connection lifecycle including initialization and cleanup.\n\n#### Scenario: Close method\n- **GIVEN** an active Redis connection\n- **WHEN** `Close()` is called\n- **THEN** the Redis client connection is closed","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775853546237,"end":1775853546242}}}}
